      "statement": "theorem procedural_AddMonoidHom_map_mul_iff_be91e71d003c : True \u2192\n  ((\u2200 {R : Type _} {S : Type _} [NonUnitalNonAssocSemiring R] [NonUnitalNonAssocSemiring S] (f : R \u2192+ S),\n    (\u2200 (x y : R), f (x * y) = f x * f y) \u2194 AddMonoidHom.mul.compr\u2082 f = (AddMonoidHom.mul.comp f).compl\u2082 f)) := by\n  sorry",
